sentences: Andreas Stevens) is an acid jazz DJ from San Diego, California now residing in Long Beach, California.

In 2009 Greyboy founded his own record label "Soundlock Recordings" as well as a turntable band called "Warchurch" members include Delmos Wade, DJ Truly Odd, Erick Coomes, Tycoon, Mike Long and Opie Ortiz.
In 2010 he released a co-produced album with Delmos Wade titled From the Ground Up.
